{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-jsx","path":"/posts/tmux-guide","webpackCompilationHash":"8124dcb5a67addf62eaf","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"dongjinjo","subtitle":"Blog by dongjinjo","copyright":"© All rights reserved.","menu":[{"label":"Articles","path":"/"},{"label":"Categories","path":"/categories/"},{"label":"Tags","path":"/tags/"}],"author":{"name":"dongjin jo","twitter":"#"},"disqusShortname":"dongjinjo","url":"https://dongjinjo.github.io"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"434972af-dacb-5fa3-9cb6-43082a4f21dd","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>tmux(terminal multiplexer) 구성 방법 및 단축키 정리</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>1.tmux 설치</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> tmux</code></pre></div>\n<h2>2.tmux 용어 정리</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>sessions : tmux 기본 실행 단위</li>\n<li>windows : session에 존재하는 탭</li>\n<li>panes : windows 내에서 화면을 분할 하여 사용</li>\n<li>prefix : tmux 단축키를 사용하기 전에 입력해야 하는 키 조합(Default : <code class=\"language-text\">ctrl + b</code> )</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>3.tmux 단축키</h2>\n<h3>3.1.sessions</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token comment\"># session 생성</span>\ntmux\ntmux new -s <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>session name<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># session 목록 조회</span>\ntmux <span class=\"token function\">ls</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># session attach</span>\ntmux attach\ntmux attach -t <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>session name<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># session detach(session 내에서)</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>prefix<span class=\"token operator\">></span> + d\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># session 강제 종료</span>\ntmux kill-session -t <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>session name<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>3.3.windows</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token comment\"># windows 생성</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>prefix<span class=\"token operator\">></span> + c\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 윈도우 이름 변경</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>prefix<span class=\"token operator\">></span> + ,\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># window 이동</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">## next</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>prefix<span class=\"token operator\">></span> + n\n<span class=\"token comment\">## previous</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>prefix<span class=\"token operator\">></span> + p\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">## 특정 window로 이동</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>prefix<span class=\"token operator\">></span> + <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>window number<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>3.4.panes</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token comment\"># pane 분할</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">## 횡</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>prefix<span class=\"token operator\">></span> + %\n<span class=\"token comment\">## 종</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>prefix<span class=\"token operator\">></span> + \"\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># pane 이동</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">## 지정</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>prefix<span class=\"token operator\">></span> + q + <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>화면에 표시되는 숫자<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">## 순차</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>prefix<span class=\"token operator\">></span> + o\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># pane 삭제</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>prefix<span class=\"token operator\">></span> + x\nctrl + d\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># pane size 변경</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">## command prompt 진입 후(&lt;prefix> + :)</span>\nresize-pane -L <span class=\"token number\">10</span>\nresize-pane -R <span class=\"token number\">10</span>\nresize-pane -D <span class=\"token number\">10</span>\nresize-pane -U <span class=\"token number\">10</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># pane layout 변경</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>prefix<span class=\"token operator\">></span> + spacebar</code></pre></div>\n<h3>3.5. 추가 옵션</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token comment\"># pane 전체에 키입력 보내기(동시 입력)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">## command prompt 진입 후(&lt;prefix> + :)</span>\nsetw synchronize-panes</code></pre></div>\n<h2>Reference</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/tmux/tmux/wiki\">https://github.com/tmux/tmux/wiki</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://man.openbsd.org/OpenBSD-current/man1/tmux.1\">http://man.openbsd.org/OpenBSD-current/man1/tmux.1</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"categorySlug":"/categories/tmux/","tagSlugs":["/tags/linux/","/tags/shortcut/"],"slug":"/posts/tmux-guide"},"frontmatter":{"title":"tmux 사용법","tags":["linux","shortcut"],"date":"2019-10-18T00:00:00.000Z","category":"tmux","description":"tmux(terminal multiplexer) 구성 방법 및 단축키 정리"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/posts/tmux-guide"}}}